title: Stored Up Blessings | Joel Osteen
itunes:title: Stored Up Blessings | Joel Osteen
description:
When God laid out the plan for your life, He prepared everything you would need to fulfill your destiny. He’s already lined up the right people, favor and increase to get you where you’re supposed to be. 

Your best days are still ahead, and together we can make a difference in this world with the message of God's hope and love.

To give visit JoelOsteen.com/GiveHope
